definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in Central Bedfordshire district, Bedfordshire , England ( OS grid ref TL1542 ) .
A northern suburb of Weymouth , Dorset , England ( OS grid ref SZ6680 ) .
A suburban area in Limerick , County Limerick , Ireland .
